question: "Who won a gold medal at the 1976 Summer Olympics, married Kris Kardashian in 1991 and from 2007 starred in the E! reality series ""Keeping Up with the Kardashians""?"
vanilla_rag_result: Caitlyn Jenner won a gold medal at the 1976 Summer Olympics, married Kris Kardashian in 1991, and from 2007 starred in the E! reality series "Keeping Up with the Kardashians."
